name: Oppressive Enforcement
Lore: 'The Imperial fleet keeps a tight grip on the systems under its control. Abuses and excesses by local citizens are not tolerated.',
Text: 'Deploy on your side of table. Your Imperial capital starships are each destiny +1. Your Immediate Effects may deploy for free. Whenever opponent cancels your card with Sense or Alter, place that canceled card in Used Pile. (Immune to Alter.)',
